â€œItâ€™s not that they donâ€™t like it,â€ I answered. â€œI donâ€™t think they get it.â€
â€œDonâ€™t get it? The plan isnâ€™t really that complex. In fact, it is simple,â€ said the CEO, preparing to give me the quick explanation.
â€œItâ€™s not that they donâ€™t get what the plan is,â€ I said. â€œYouâ€™re right: it is simple. It reduces overall compensation for sales staff, especially for the low producers.â€
